        <div class="chocolate-bar" style="top: 15%; right: 10%; animation-delay: 1s;"></div>

        <h2 class="section-title">The Rosier Chocolate Experience</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">
            From bean to bar, we craft each protein bar with care using premium ingredients and
            rich chocolate flavors that satisfy your cravings and fuel your life.
        </p>

        <div class="gallery-grid">
            <div class="gallery-item">
                <img src="~/Content/images/Rosier_Chocolate_Making_Process.png" alt="Rosier Chocolate Making Process">
